{"title":"学习建议","uid":"af0796bc1f9f859cc896a7b3cb3c8db4","slug":"学习建议","date":"2022-08-08T12:47:40.000Z","updated":"2022-10-31T11:07:21.353Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/学习建议.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/photo-2.jpg","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><h2 id=\"学习建议\"><a href=\"#学习建议\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"学习建议\"></a>学习建议</h2><h3 id=\"搜索引擎\"><a href=\"#搜索引擎\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搜索引擎\"></a>搜索引擎</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/\">Google</a> 世界第一搜索引擎，除了别墙之外没有缺点</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/\">百度</a> 国内第一搜索引擎，但是搜不到github（也就意味着代码问题解决不了）</p>\n<h3 id=\"Markdown\"><a href=\"#Markdown\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Markdown\"></a>Markdown</h3><p><a href=\"https://markdown.com.cn/\">Markdown</a> 是一种轻量级标记语言，它允许人们使用易读易写的纯文本格式编写文档，Markdown文件的后缀名便是“.md”。<br>我感觉Markdown是世界上最棒的笔记工具了，简洁、美观、高效。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><a href=\"https://markdown.com.cn/\">markdown官方文档</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/v0.26.2/doc/Rules.md#\">markdown插件以及书写规范</a></p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"Web-学习\"><a href=\"#Web-学习\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Web 学习\"></a>Web 学习</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/\">bilibili哔哩哔哩</a> 中国的youtube，简称B站，外号B站大学，博客的搭建也是在B站诸多视频的参考下建立的</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/\">MDN Web Docs</a> Web的官方文档，有最先进的标准和语法规定</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.w3school.com.cn/\">W3school</a> W3C，国内知名网站技术在线学习平台</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.runoob.com/\">菜鸟教程</a> 菜鸟教程，非常适合新手、菜鸟、小白的网站技术在线学习平台</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://valine.js.org/\">valine &amp; i18n</a> 无后台评论系统，用于博客配套使用</p>\n<h3 id=\"GitHub\"><a href=\"#GitHub\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"GitHub\"></a>GitHub</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.github.com/\">全球最大同性交友网站</a> GitHub 是一个面向开源及私有软件项目的托管平台，因为只支持Git作为唯一的版本库格式进行托管，故名GitHub。</p>\n<h3 id=\"Gitee-码云\"><a href=\"#Gitee-码云\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Gitee 码云\"></a>Gitee 码云</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.gitee.com/\">Gitee码云</a>  中国版的GitHub，Gitee 基于Git的代码托管服务，Gitee是开源中国（OSChina）推出的基于Git的代码托管服务平台。</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>Tip</summary>\n<p>除了服务器在国内，可以说GitHub的优点他是一个没学到，开放度差，大量的审核机制，并且不能做图床，而且Gitee Pages总会有些莫名其妙的BUG</p>\n\n</details>\n","feature":false,"text":"我个人对计算机知识的一些学习技巧以及方法，还有一些常用的网站之类的，让大伙见笑了。仅供参考~","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":660,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"study","slug":"study","count":5,"path":"api/categories/study.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"学习","slug":"学习","count":5,"path":"api/tags/学习.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">学习建议</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">搜索引擎</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Markdown\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Markdown</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Web-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Web 学习</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#GitHub\"><span class=\"toc-text\">GitHub</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Gitee-%E7%A0%81%E4%BA%91\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Gitee 码云</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"LuiYang","slug":"luiyang","avatar":"/img/head.jpg","link":"/img/head.jpg","description":"<p>与其临渊羡鱼，不如退而结网<p>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/LuiYang08","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/13888214?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0"},"gitee":{"icon":"/svg/gitee.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/luiyang"},"mail":{"icon":"/svg/mail.svg","link":"mailto:206614221@qq.com"},"qq":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://jq.qq.com/?_wv=1027&k=zYcHMcp1"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"搭建博客-图文教程","uid":"fc5bc12ca65b83e4039a8c46b5c3ce57","slug":"Build Blog","date":"2022-09-29T08:28:00.0